OOC: Hey Dcoburn! Great to see you again! Can i keep Wheeljack? So far ive 
had him make the Iron Fists sheilds really powerful, and he got involved in a 
battle. If you want him back, thats alright too. Jason, what are you talking 
about? Herald was NEVER involved with the TM3's. Zardus is right. And dont 
say i have no authority, because Shomin is a good friend of mine, and he 
always told me his plots.  Well, the TM2s always needed a driver, and the 
driver wasnt my idea, it was good ol' Minime. Thanks anyway for Tigerhawk and 
Depth Charge.


--part1_b8.10bb2f9a.279a89d8_boundary
